From cd84afdb92b55be7890af70f21f735152309d304 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Tue, 21 Jul 2026 18:45:30 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Adiciona comprovante de entrega Onfleet (fotos + assinatura)

As fotos e a assinatura tiradas pelo motorista na conclusao ficam em
task.completionDetails (photoUploadIds / photoUploadId / signatureUploadId).
O backend agora monta as URLs publicas no CDN da Onfleet e devolve nos campos
`fotos` e `assinatura`; o front-end exibe uma galeria "Comprovante de entrega"
com as miniaturas e a assinatura, com lightbox para ampliar.

- rastrear.js: extrai photoUploadIds/photoUploadId/signatureUploadId e monta as
  URLs https://d15p8tr8p0vffz.cloudfront.net/<id>/800x.png (foto) e /282x.png (assinatura)
- index.html: secao de comprovante com grid de fotos, assinatura e lightbox;
  imagens que nao carregam sao removidas automaticamente

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 index.html                    | 83 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 netlify/functions/rastrear.js | 15 +++++++
 2 files changed, 98 insertions(+)

diff --git a/index.html b/index.html
index e6a2b4f..e1e4cbf 100644
